{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","data":{"alias":"sodalite-aquatic-bluegill","description":"## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Confirm + document that GitHub branch CI runs on main after Gerrit replication (the free semantic-conflict detector) — where it lives, what it gates.\n- [ ] Add a short runbook (infra/runbooks/) for 'main is red post-merge': identify the culprit change, revert via Gerrit, land the revert.\n- [ ] Note auto-revert is deliberately NOT built (cost/scope); revisit only if red-main recurs.\n- [ ] Cross-link from the ADR + CONTRIBUTING.","id":"f542-17bf-1c43-4ce1","parent_id":"d4de-7d65-2a96-48be","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Document post-merge safety net + manual-revert runbook"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783986511846831001,"uuid":"d6a448ab-59b9-4364-8116-26c33f718896"}